claim.claim-text:
A base station as set forth in claim 1, wherein

the setting unit (15) is configured to set the dedicated frequency bands indicated by the frequency band information and set as an dedicated extension bands;

the transmission unit (13) is configured to transmit mainly further dedicated data information via the dedicated extension band.

A mobile communication system as set forth in claim 10, wherein

the transmission unit (13) configured to transmit the specific frequency band information and/or the dedicated frequency band information in advance;

a receiving unit (22) configured to receive the specific frequency band information and/or the dedicated frequency band information before a change of specific frequency bands.
